'''乳清蛋白'''（[[英文|英文]]：'''Whey Protein'''）是由[[乳清|乳清]]（生产[[干酪|干酪]]所产生的液体副产品）當中提煉出來的一種[[球状蛋白质|球状蛋白质]]混合物。

乳清蛋白常作为[[膳食補充劑|膳食補充劑]]出售和使用。

== 生产 ==
{{main|乳清}}
生产干酪时，牛奶凝结后所剩的液体叫做乳清，牛奶凝结过程中[[pH值|pH值]]降到4.6以后所有可溶物都留在乳清中<ref>{{cite web|last1=Spurlock|first1=D|title=Isolation and Identification of Casein From Milk Course Notes|url=http://homepages.ius.edu/dspurloc/c122/casein.htm|accessdate=27 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616003735/http://homepages.ius.edu/dspurloc/c122/casein.htm|archivedate=2014年6月16日}}</ref>。溶液含有5%的[[乳糖|乳糖]]，还有一些[[矿物质|矿物质]]和{{link-en|乳清白蛋白|lactalbumin}}<ref name="brit">"Whey." The Encyclopædia Britannica. 15th ed. 1994</ref>。溶液中的脂肪分离后可加工成为食品<ref name="brit"/>。分离方法可以是简单的干燥，也可以是去除[[油脂|油脂]]等其他物质来增加蛋白质浓度<ref name=Foegeding>{{Cite journal
 | title = Advances in modifying and understanding whey protein functionality
 | year = 2002
 | journal = Trends in Food Science & Technology
 | pages = 151–9
 | volume = 13
 | issue = 5
 | last1 =Foegeding | first1 =EA
 | last2 =Davis | first2 =JP
 | last3 =Doucet | first3 =D
 | last4 =McGuffey | first4 =MK
 | doi=10.1016/S0924-2244(02)00111-5
}}</ref>。例如，在{{link-en|膜过滤|membrane filtration }}后使用{{link-en|喷雾干燥|spray drying}}可分离乳清中的蛋白质<ref>{{cite book |author=Tunick MH |year=2008 |chapter=Whey Protein Production and Utilization. |editor=Onwulata CI, Huth PJ |title=Whey processing, functionality and health benefits |place=Ames, Iowa |publisher=Blackwell Publishing; IFT Press |pages=1–13 |url=http://www.ars.usda.gov/research/publications/Publications.htm?seq_no_115=209388 |format=abstract |access-date=2015-09-10 |archive-date=2008-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024002711/http://www.ars.usda.gov/research/publications/Publications.htm?seq_no_115=209388 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

加热可使乳清[[变性_(生物化学)|变性]]。加强热（如[[巴氏消毒法|巴氏消毒法]]中持续加热超过72度）可使乳清蛋白变性。[[凝乳酶|凝乳酶]]作用和牛奶[[酸|酸]]化并不会使天然乳清蛋白变性。乳清蛋白变性后会和别的蛋白质发生[[疏水作用|疏水作用]]，形成蛋白质[[凝胶|凝胶]]。<ref name=Foegeding/> 受热变性的乳清蛋白仍然会使有些人过敏。<ref name=Lee/>

== 成分 ==
乳清蛋白是从[[乳清|乳清]]中分离的[[球状蛋白质|球状蛋白质]]的总称。牛奶中的蛋白质中20％是乳清蛋白，另外80％是[[酪蛋白|酪蛋白]]<ref>{{Cite journal|author= Jay R. Hoffman and Michael J. Falvo |journal= Journal of Sports Science and Medicine |year=2004 |issue=3 |pages=118–130 |title=Protein - Which is best?}}</ref>；人乳中的蛋白质中60％是乳清蛋白，40％是酪蛋白<ref>{{cite journal | author=Luhovyy BL, Akhavan T, Anderson GH | title=Whey proteins in the regulation of food intake and satiety | journal=Journal of the American College of Nutrition | volume=26 | issue=6 | year=2007 | pages=704S–712S | url=http://www.jacn.org/cgi/content/full/26/6/704S | id= | pmid=18187437 | doi=10.1080/07315724.2007.10719651 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110326192331/http://www.jacn.org/cgi/content/full/26/6/704S | archivedate=2011-03-26 | access-date=2015-09-10 }}</ref>。乳清中的蛋白质占固体总量的10%。乳清蛋白的主要成分为{{link-en|β-乳球蛋白|beta-lactoglobulin}}（约65%）、{{link-en|α-乳白蛋白|alpha-lactalbumin}}（约25%）、[[牛血清白蛋白|牛血清白蛋白]]（约8%，另见[[血清白蛋白|血清白蛋白]]）、还有[[免疫球蛋白|免疫球蛋白]]<ref>{{cite journal
